<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Personal Portfolio: Professional Trader Trainer</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --dark-bg: #121212;
            --dark-surface: #1e1e1e;
            --accent-purple: #9c27b0;
            --accent-gold: #ffc107;
            --text-light: #e0e0e0;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--dark-bg);
            color: var(--text-light);
            line-height: 1.6;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* --- Header & Nav --- */
        nav {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            width: 100%;
            background-color: rgba(18, 18, 18, 0.95);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 1rem 5%;
            z-index: 1000;
        }

        .logo-nav {
            height: 50px;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 0 10px var(--accent-purple));
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            list-style: none;
        }

        .nav-links li {
            margin-left: 1.5rem;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--text-light);
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover {
            color: var(--accent-purple);
        }

        /* --- Hero Section (The Visionary) --- */
        #hero {
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 0 10%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at center, rgba(156, 39, 176, 0.2), transparent);
        }

        .hero-container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 2rem;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .hero-img-container {
            width: 300px;
            height: 300px;
            overflow: hidden;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 4px solid var(--accent-purple);
            filter: drop-shadow(0 0 15px rgba(156, 39, 176, 0.6));
        }

        .hero-img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .hero-content {
            max-width: 600px;
        }

        .hero-content h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: white;
            line-height: 1.1;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .hero-content p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            color: #b0bec5;
        }

        .btn-gold {
            background-color: var(--accent-gold);
            color: #212121;
            padding: 10px 25px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
        }

        .btn-gold:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(255, 193, 7, 0.4);
        }

        /* --- Keahlian Section (Practitioner's Lab) --- */
        #keahlian {
            background-color: var(--dark-surface);
            padding: 5rem 10%;
            text-align: center;
        }

        #keahlian h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            color: white;
        }

        .keahlian-container {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 2rem;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .keahlian-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border-radius: 10px;
            width: 300px;
            padding: 2rem;
            border-left: 3px solid transparent;
            transition: background 0.3s, border-left 0.3s;
        }

        .keahlian-card:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            border-left: 3px solid var(--accent-purple);
        }

        .keahlian-card img {
            width: 50px;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        /* --- Gallery Section (Focus Zone) --- */
        #gallery {
            padding: 5rem 10%;
        }

        .gallery-item {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }

        .gallery-item.reverse {
            flex-direction: row-reverse;
        }

        .gallery-item-img {
            width: 50%;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
        }

        .gallery-item-img img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .gallery-item-content {
            width: 50%;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        /* --- Contact Section --- */
        #contact {
            background-color: var(--dark-surface);
            padding: 5rem 10%;
            text-align: center;
        }

        #contact img.contact-accent {
            width: 80px;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 0 10px var(--accent-purple));
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        #contact form {
            max-width: 500px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        input, textarea {
            width: 100%;
            background: var(--dark-bg);
            border: 1px solid #333;
            color: var(--text-light);
            padding: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        /* Responsive Mobile */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero-container {
                flex-direction: column;
                text-align: center;
            }

            .gallery-item {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .gallery-item-img {
                width: 100%;
            }

            .gallery-item-content {
                width: 100%;
                text-align: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
    </head>
<body>

    <nav>
        <img src="logo.png" alt="Logo" class="logo-nav">
        <ul class="nav-links">
            <li><a href="#hero">About</a></li>
            <li><a href="#keahlian">Services</a></li>
            <li><a href="#gallery">Focus</a></li>
            <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>

    <section id="hero">
        <div class="hero-container">
            <div class="hero-img-container">
                <img src="wajah.jpg" alt="[Nama Anda]" class="hero-img">
            </div>
            <div class="hero-content">
                <h1>Menguasai Pasar dari Ruang Kerja Minimalis.</h1>
                <p>Saya membantu Anda, professional trader, menavigasi kompleksitas chart dengan disiplin, data, dan mindset yang tepat.</p>
                <a href="#contact" class="btn-gold">Konsultasi Gratis</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="keahlian">
        <h2>Saya Tidak Hanya Mengajar. Saya Hidup di Chart.</h2>
        <div class="keahlian-container">
            <div class="keahlian-card">
                <h3>Analisis Real-Time</h3>
                <p>Membaca data candlestick di dua monitor untuk eksekusi terbaik.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="keahlian-card">
                <h3>Mindset & Disiplin</h3>
                <p>Membangun psikologi trading yang kuat seperti "Believe in Yourself".</p>
            </div>
            <div class="keahlian-card">
                <h3>Professional Coaching</h3>
                <p>Sesi 1-on-1 untuk menaikkan level strategi profesional Anda.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="gallery">
        <div class="gallery-item">
            <div class="gallery-item-img">
                <img src="keahlian.jpg" alt="Trading Setup">
            </div>
            <div class="gallery-item-content">
                <h3>The Practitioner's Lab</h3>
                <p>Di sinilah keahlian teknis saya diuji. Setup trading dengan grafik yang terus bergerak dan kincir ria cahaya, tempat saya menajamkan intuisi analisis pasar.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="gallery-item reverse">
            <div class="gallery-item-img">
                <img src="pendukung.jpg" alt="Focus Zone">
            </div>
            <div class="gallery-item-content">
                <h3>The Focus Zone</h3>
                <p>Suasana yang gelap namun fokus. Kincir ria menyinari ruang kerja saya saat pasar bergerak intens. Di sinilah disiplin dan ketahanan diuji.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="contact">
        <img src="logo.png" alt="Logo Aksen" class="contact-accent">
        <h2>Mulaienaikkan Level Trading Anda?</h2>
        <form>
            <input type="text" placeholder="Nama Anda" required>
            <input type="email" placeholder="Email Anda" required>
            <textarea placeholder="Pesan Anda" rows="5" required></textarea>
            <button type="submit" class="btn-gold">Kirim Pesan</button>
        </form>
    </section>

</body>
</html>
